# M1 CLI eval round (2026-05-23) — entire directory is local-only.
# Contains real-account traces (UHostIds, IPs, prices, trace_id), GT JSON
# dumps, and raw_results.json. Older rounds (round2 etc.) committed a
# hand-curated subset of *.md reports; this round was run as a developer
# regression check only, so the whole directory stays untracked. If a
# sanitized summary is needed later, copy it out to docs/ first.
eval/shadow_qa/2026-05-23-m1-cli-eval/
# M2 CLI eval round (2026-05-24) — same policy as M1. Reply / tool-call
# regression check only. CLI path does not hydrate SessionState so the
# eval does NOT cover M2's RecentFacts / SelectedInstance / LastIntent
# writers; those are covered by engine unit/integration tests and the
# HTTP fact-persist e2e test.
eval/shadow_qa/2026-05-24-m2-cli-eval/
# PR-β multi-region CLI eval round (2026-05-25). Live AK/SK + LLM key in
# agent.yaml; questions reference real instance UHostIds. Reply / tool-call
# regression check only — covers cross-region mutating workflow Region wiring.
eval/shadow_qa/2026-05-25-prb-region-cli-eval/
